 all supplementary features and functionalities of the applications using the basic top navigation bars."]},"id":"841385fd-731c-4033-9115-735c9cb05563","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Help &amp; Support"},"id":"8fd0866f-80c6-4c71-bc1f-b1f149ac76af","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/bibKdwP4XZ2uC2gBx5sWQo.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Like most Blu-ray to DVD converter software, Xilisoft offers technical support that&#39;s average at best. The manufacturer&#39;s website has a comprehensive tutorial and FAQs for the DVD Creator but oddly nothing for its Blu-ray ripper. It does, however, provide a handful of email addresses and an online contact form that you can use to contact Xilisoft. We sent a customer inquiry to the company via email and were pleasantly surprised when we received a response within 24 hours. One thing we&#39;d like to see on the website that our other top-ranked products have is discussion boards or a user forum where you can ask technical questions and receive feedback from other users of the application.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/50899-xilisoft-blu-ray-to-dvd-converter12.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bibKdwP4XZ2uC2gBx5sWQo.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"bibKdwP4XZ2uC2gBx5sWQo","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/bibKdwP4XZ2uC2gBx5sWQo.jpg","alt":""},"id":"f4b5d483-3f6c-45a0-b344-8847b476cc86","type":"image"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"93e9621b-4b45-4ea4-8ac7-69649a9119ba","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Our biggest contention with this otherwise excellent Blu-ray to DVD converter software is its lack of built-in decryption. While some users may not consider it an issue, we feel you shouldn&#39;t have to pay extra on top of the purchase price just to make the software actually work. That being said, its unmatched output quality and multifaceted functionality are superb and make Xilisoft Blu-ray to DVD Converter a top contender.